# Auth invariants (mirror of AGENTS.md + docs/guides/auth-invariants.md)

- Server authorization uses `getClaims()`, not `getSession()`.
- Session refresh belongs in root `proxy.ts` via `@workspace/supabase-auth/proxy/update-session`.
- Validate route/action inputs at the boundary with shared schemas when the boundary is reusable.
- Sensitive auth-adjacent handlers should call the abuse-protection hook before external auth work.
